spec_data.Name: perl-ModelSim-List
spec_data.Description:
This module provides a class named ModelSim::List with which the EDA tester
can easily check in the signals contained in the files generated by
ModelSim's "write list" command in a programming manner.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 01:21:01 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Analyse the 'list' output of the ModelSim simulator
